{"tid":2497194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子前年以渠蓋襲擊清理路障市民　判監三年四個月","createTime":"2021-04-20T10:45:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T11:35:25.000Z","uid":283837,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"abe153cd52971b689e1ec5045774796c638b282a","tid":2497194,"uid":283837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:45:29.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】一名裝修判頭承認，前年在旺角以渠蓋襲擊一名清理示威路障的人，被判監三年四個月。<br />\n<br />\n案發在2019年12月1日，有市民在旺角一帶集結堵路，期間一名市民上前搬開路障，被人用渠蓋擊向頭部後倒下，送院後頭部要縫十針。<br />\n<br />\n報稱裝修判頭的被告梁啟樂，在區域法院承認一項有意圖而傷人罪，他在求情信中表示，對事件感到後悔，願意向事主作出賠償，法官練錦鴻判處被告監禁三年四個月，及向事主賠償2萬元。<br />\n<br />\n警方對判刑表示歡迎，認為能充分反映案情嚴重性及具有一定阻嚇性。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=431772\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D431772&d=aLufatioEIfsHY%2FyaDEQJ84e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=962f1648\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D431772&h=b23413f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=431772</a>"},{"pid":"c6536ebd584a19d4c7bc68d6a403ef1ce3a90a04","tid":2497194,"uid":33728,"like":2,"dislike":17,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:46:21.000Z","msg":"抵死"},{"pid":"e7771cc214306b1d7ba6287c0144f0f8c4d829f1","tid":2497194,"uid":7369,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:47:10.000Z","msg":"已封鎖會員 - 麥樂雞獸v3"},{"pid":"e168dec1f380e167229d005c17096e8bed5659c8","tid":2497194,"uid":83060,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:47:22.000Z","msg":"英雄"},{"pid":"14105f1c4cf38d77565a3d99cb6c788179f2963f","tid":2497194,"uid":183844,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T10:47:39.000Z","msg":"將軍澳斬3人都係3年幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9da0165e69ac8e3f9e278fa40eb1e46e88592b9c","tid":2497194,"uid":33263,"like":2,"dislike":2,"scor